headline: Dell Technologies Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: ROUND ROCK, Texas, June 17, 2025--Dell Technologies (NYSE: DELL) announces that its board of directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.525 per common share, which will be payable on Aug. 1 to shareholders of record as of July 22.
